  "title": "SPECIALIST CLINIC MANAGER",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Assist in the clinic’s day to day operations and functions.</li>\n  <li>Assist the Medical Director in the assigned clinic.</li>\n  <li>Responsible for all aspects of customer service including but not limited to cashiering, appointment booking, and answering customer enquiries.</li>\n  <li>Responsible for all matters pertaining to insurance, Medisave, and Letter of Guarantee(s).</li>\n  <li>Liaise with customers, vendors, suppliers, and local regulatory bodies when required.</li>\n  <li>Assist in the renewal of government licenses including but not limited to Clinic License, Fire, Insurance, and HSA.</li>\n  <li>Other duties assigned by your reporting officer as required.</li>\n</ul>",
